Is just great against burst. I'm not sure if it's actually needed or not, due to the insane power creeping in terms of burst, but it's a lot of pseudo-mitigation and it's, personally, welcome in a game where it takes ages to kill tanks.

Other than that, just wait for {{champion:38}} and {{champion:75}} to get {{item:1054}} nerfed.
